export enum MassUploadStatus {
  PROCESSING = "Processing",
  PENDING_APPROVAL = "Pending Approval",
  PENDING_APPROVAL_CONFLICT = "Pending Approval (Conflict)",
  APPROVED = "Approved",
  COMPLETED = "Completed",
  COMPLETED_CONFLICT = "Completed (Conflict)",
  FAILED_VERIFIER_ACTION = "Failed: Verifier Action",
  REJECTED = "Rejected"
}

export enum MassUploadType {
  KR = "KAH/RNSA",
  FA = "Flying/Aircrew",
  SB = "Shipboard",
  DI = "Diving"
}
